# Vercel zero-config treats any file in `/api/` at the project root as a
# Python (or Node, depending on extension) serverless function. For this
# project, the FastAPI under `api/index.py` is deployed as a SEPARATE
# Vercel project (root-dir = `./`, framework = Other) — we don't want
# the frontend's deploy to also try to bundle it. Excluding here is
# defence-in-depth on top of setting `Root Directory = apps/web` in
# the Vercel project settings.
api/

# Local dev artefacts that should never reach the deploy.
*.log
.DS_Store
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
